      <title>独家：中国、阿联酋、土耳其加强银行审查，俄罗斯难以收取石油付款</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/russia-struggles-collect-oil-payments-china-uae-turkey-raise-bank-scrutiny-2024-03-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[八位知情人士称，由于中国、土耳其和阿联酋的银行对美国的二级制裁变得更加谨慎，俄罗斯石油公司的原油和燃料付款面临长达几个月的延迟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/russia-struggles-collect-oil-payments-china-uae-turkey-raise-bank-scrutiny-2024-03-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 06:04:24 GMT</pubDate>
